README
=======
This search engine is used to index files in your server 
and enables you to search it at ease. The following 
points have to be noted before you use the search engine :

(*) When you're using the search engine for the first time,
go to the ./install/ directory to start the installation 
process. This might take a while.

(*) Once this is done, you can go to the search engine and 
begin by entering your search term.